name: JBL Endurance Run - Earphones with mic - in-ear - wired - black | Dell USA
description: JBL Endurance RUN is a wired earphone with IPX5 sweatproof rating and a tangle-free cord with remote and microphone so users can take calls and listen to music while hiking or on a jog through the neighborhood. Its FlipHook design provides flexibility to wear both in-ear and behind-the-ear.
